## ğŸ“Œ Important Routes

### Admin Routes

* `GET /admin/signup` â†’ Admin signup form
* `POST /admin/signup` â†’ Create admin
* `GET /admin/signin` â†’ Admin login form
* `POST /admin/signin` â†’ Login admin
* `GET /create/courses` â†’ Render course creation form
* `POST /create/courses` â†’ Create new course
* `GET /update/course` â†’ Render update form
* `POST /update/course` â†’ Update course
* `GET /courses` â†’ List admin's courses

### User Routes

* `GET /signup` â†’ User signup form
* `POST /signup` â†’ Create user
* `GET /signin` â†’ User login form
* `POST /signin` â†’ Login user
* `GET /purchase` â†’ Render purchase form
* `POST /purchase` â†’ Purchase a course
* `GET /purchases` â†’ List purchased courses

